    "description": "<strong>Marble Havoc</strong> is a 3D-action game. Take your marble in different levels to the goal.<br><br>You start with your marble on a way in a waterland. Navigate your marble over the way without falling into the water.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205160/extras/370ae34d46157d246179c12c38ca2421.avif?t=1752607555\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205160/extras_big/370ae34d46157d246179c12c38ca2421.avif?t=1752607555 width=800 height=678 /></span><br><br>Jump over obstacles and ditches. Find the flag. Your mission is to navigate your marble to the flag and hit the flag pole. Then you mastered the level.<br><br>You are not alone! In the waterland there are other marbles on their way:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205160/extras/55d71962d8461cff038fadd622955e4e.avif?t=1752607555\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205160/extras_big/55d71962d8461cff038fadd622955e4e.avif?t=1752607555 width=800 height=748 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unfriendly red marbles want to kick you off the way into the water. Avoid any contact with them.<br></li><li> The green marbles try to push the red marbles away.</li></ul>",
